{ type: install
  message: <<EOM
To run the game, make a local copy of /usr/local/share/vangers/data
directory in ~/.vangers and then copy the game content in "data"
directory from a Steam installation into ~/.vangers/data and run:

$ vangers-run

The source code of this game is a mess, so be prepared to face
probable bugs.
EOM
}
